Package com.norswap.nanoeth.trees.patricia.memory

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    MemPatriciaBranchNode
    A branch node in the in-memory patricia tree.
    MemPatriciaDigestNode
    This is a special kind of node that never occurs in a normal patricia trie, but is used to facilitate the verification of Merkle proofs.
    MemPatriciaExtensionNode
    This in-memory patricia tree node represents a shared sequence of nibbles between multiples keys (a "key fragment").
    MemPatriciaLeafNode
    A leaf in the in-memory patrica tree, which store the suffix of the key and its associated data.
    MemPatriciaNode
    The common interface for all in-memory patricia tree node implementations.
